>"},{"pid":"ee9960276fef3fb9ae18beefec4e8b9ed7e56413","tid":277800,"uid":89478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>藍球本身唔垃圾，但nba呢個組織好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聯盟為左幫foj造神<br />\nD規則改到有咁西得咁西+必要時安排埋黑哨配合<br />\n搞到nba睇到一肚氣<br />\n<br />\n利申：自從foj去熱水組巨頭之後已經無咩點睇nba</blockquote><br />\nlbj係神話 妒人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n散步撚講野好好笑<br />\n<br />\n話人組巨頭 不如話巴塞皇馬曼組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咁用錢買人 組得仲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c62db36573175e1652024fa078d15f8e1323078","tid":277800,"uid":89478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇左幾耐波呀<br />\nPO仲要final三個鐘有幾奇<br />\n強度咁高<br />\n雞聲一定多</blockquote><br />\n成日暫停又有得抖<br />\n強度有幾高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆過下都用曬你啲力啦 傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969cc5422585e42c1c0b4bc5d4abecaebd068d1c","tid":277800,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係打40分鐘 但有120分鐘休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為打得辛苦 多時間抖係合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251d9c6358bfba82b308927f3ed408ab56326e1b","tid":277800,"uid":89478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇左幾耐波呀<br />\nPO仲要final三個鐘有幾奇<br />\n強度咁高<br />\n雞聲一定多</blockquote><br />\n成日暫停又有得抖<br />\n強度有幾高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強度高，多接觸多foul<br />\nft佔好多時間，to呢啲當然都佔多時間</blockquote><br />\n總共打48分鐘<br />\n180-48=132<br />\n一場波入面抖左兩個幾鐘<img src=\